title: Filippo Dal Moro
text:
Filippo Dal Moro (born 11 August 1970 in <a href="Treviso">Treviso</a>) is a retired <a href="Italy">Italian</a> professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
He played 2 seasons in the <a href="Serie%20A">Serie A</a> for <a href="A.S.%20Roma">A.S. Roma</a> (12 games). He also played for Roma in the <a href="UEFA%20Cup">UEFA Cup</a> in the 1998/99 season.
